    comment: '<p>Highlighted text area colors can be easily change with the <code>::selection</code> pseudo element.</p>\n<p>Apply <code>::selection</code> on a paragraph:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-css">p::selection {\n  background: black;\n  color: white;\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>Gecko is the only engine requiring the prefix, so adding an other rule is required to support all browsers :</p>\n<pre><code class="language-css">p::-moz-selection {\n  background: black;\n  color: white;\n}\n</code></pre>\n',
